Name: TOUGE RACERS
About the game: Touge Racers is a single-play racing game. It is a race battle on the pass with the old car team that I met at the pass. A racing game where you can drift down a winding road. It is a game where you win the game and accumulate points to remodel the car. The color of the car can be changed freely. You can also use points to buy the car of the opponent who won the game.
